Details of who contributed what can be found in the ChangeLog history. Special
mention:

"Lac":
- significant improvements to the original wx version, including major changes
to the edit card dialog (searching, speedups, etc), and mac specific fixes
- built and maintained the mac version until fc became anki, and offered lots
of useful input into how things work on the mac.
- improved hiragana generation with kakasi
- wrote most of the original kanji stats

"Iroiro":
- a number of bugfixes, most of the original kanji occurrences code

"Frostschutz":
- some bugfixes, lots of testing, and constantly trying to donate

All of the translators have been a great help, too:

* Laurent Steffan
* Andreas Klauer
* "Pcsl"
